Question: Shenzhen Highstar Electrical Co., Ltd. CES 2024 product highlight and specification
Summary:
Shenzhen Highstar Electrical Co., Ltd.

CES 2024 Product Highlight:

- Manufacturer of LED reading lamps, lantern speakers, and promotion gifts.
- Owns a 7,500 square meter industrial park with 7 assembly/production lines.
- ISO9001:2015 certified with products having CE, EMC, FCC, LVD, and RoHS certifications.
- Participates in various exhibitions including the American International Consumer Electronics Show.
- Products sold in various regions worldwide.
- Offers OEM and ODM projects.
- Specializes in electronic transformers, chokes, SMD power inductors, and magnetic components.
- ISO9001 certified with a strong design team and reliability testing equipment.
- Contact: Cicely Wu (Tel: +86 135 3425 8018, E-mail: cicely@szhighstar.com) and David Wen (E-mail: davidwen@szhighstar.com, Tel/WhatsApp: +86 159 1539 7626).
- Office Address: 502, Huashenghui Building, 15 Jinhai Road, Baoan District, Shenzhen City, Guangdong.
- Factory Address: Building 3, Yaowangxing Industrial Park, Dayawan West District, Huizhou City, Guangdong Province.
